			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Here's a question for those high level clerics to expound upon.  What are some good clerical items to shoot for at various levels?  I'm looking mainly for some guildlines.  IE, when should I reasonably expect to start looking for Bronze armour.  What should I shoot for after that?  What jewelry or specialty items best suits a cleric and at what level do I have a reasonable chance of getting it?  I know this varies a lot depending upon how good you are at auctioning and getting money.  There are so many items running around it's hard to keep up with all of them.  Even a list of good clerical items with suggested prices would help.  <BR>
<BR>
Thanks in advance.<BR>
<BR>
Clangedin<BR>
14th level priest of Brell<BR>
Prexus and Karana servers.
				</font>
